00:42:56,660 --> 00:42:59,530
Jangan terlalu penasaran soal urusan orang lain.

747
00:43:00,359 --> 00:43:01,559
Kembalilah bekerja.

748
00:43:03,030 --> 00:43:04,029
Baik.

749
00:44:36,159 --> 00:44:37,830
"Do Ran, ayah pergi ke toko roti"

