00:44:37,830 --> 00:44:39,629
"Menyarap dan istirahatlah"

751
00:44:48,899 --> 00:44:55,180
"Roti Ayah"

752
00:45:00,249 --> 00:45:02,519
Pak, Anda sedang apa?

753
00:45:03,119 --> 00:45:05,889
Bukan apa-apa.

754
00:45:05,889 --> 00:45:06,989
Tunggu.

755
00:45:07,420 --> 00:45:10,129
Anda membersihkan bagian depan toko?

756
00:45:11,229 --> 00:45:12,960
Mengelap jendela juga?

757
00:45:13,100 --> 00:45:14,759
Itu...

758
00:45:15,600 --> 00:45:17,670
Kamu selalu menawariku roti,

759
00:45:18,529 --> 00:45:20,940
