950
00:55:37,449 --> 00:55:38,719
Jangan khawatir.

951
00:55:39,149 --> 00:55:40,560
Akan ibu selesaikan ini.

952
00:55:46,659 --> 00:55:48,300
Benarkah itu, Ibu?

953
00:55:48,859 --> 00:55:51,070
Kak Do Ran mungkin akan bercerai?

954
00:55:53,000 --> 00:55:54,600
